Title: Hvis du er trist er jeg trist
Actors: Iman Meskini, Ina Svenningdal, Josefine Frida Pettersen, Ulrikke Falch
Plot: Sana suspects that Sara is hiding something from her. Sana's mother is worried about her recent behavior, which Sana finds very irritating. Elias then reaches out to Sana and gives her some advice. Everyone gathers for a karaoke party.
